  "notes": "The .ugkeybg div is always inside #main on UG course pages. The .sticky-ctas div always carries the class 'on-load'. Buttons in .buttons use the .uosbutton class (UosButton atom); some also carry 'apply-button' as an additional className. Each .stickybutton contains an <i> with the Font Awesome icon class followed by the label text. The .altentry span is conditionally rendered only when an alternate year link is provided. The .fb-award-duration class is reused across duration, startDate and attendance value spans. Feature list items that are false should not be rendered. The .fy feature class (sandwich year, featureSandwichYear prop) appears on 126 pages. The 'study-abroad-option' and 'study-abroad' are distinct features (optional vs confirmed study abroad).",
  "htmlExamples": ["3833_1950", "3833_1949", "3833_1738", "3833_1945"]
}
